---
// Standing CTA at the end of every FHB blog post.
// Edit copy here in one place to update across the whole blog.
---

<aside class="my-12 px-6 py-10 lg:px-10 lg:py-12 rounded-2xl text-center" style="background-color: #fdf2f5; border: 1px solid #f9d6e0;">
	<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #a04060; font-family: var(--font-sans);">
		Partner with the Father's Heart Bible
	</p>
	<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-tight max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-ink);">
		Help bring the Father's Heart Bible to every nation.
	</h2>
	<p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-muted);">
		Your generous gift today supports the translation, the publishing, and the global distribution of FHB &mdash; a Bible meant to reach every reader who longs to know the Father, in every language and every people group.
	</p>
	<a
		href="/partner/"
		class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-7 px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold no-underline transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
		style="background-color: var(--color-brand); color: #ffffff; font-family: var(--font-sans);"
	>
		Partner with FHB
		<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
	</a>
</aside>
